      <title>疯狂星期一过后，交易员纷纷对冲极端市场事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/black-swan-hedging-breaks-out-on-wall-street-after-manic-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们纷纷为自己的投资组合投保，以防范极端的市场崩盘，这与疫情开始时的混乱时期如出一辙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/black-swan-hedging-breaks-out-on-wall-street-after-manic-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
